00:27:27.310 --> 00:27:28.930
Every single thing
I've ever done

00:27:28.930 --> 00:27:31.060
is about the notion
of opposites.

00:27:31.060 --> 00:27:33.730
The paradoxical
men, women, east,

00:27:33.730 --> 00:27:36.580
west, mysticism, and violence.

00:27:36.580 --> 00:27:42.310
And "Woman Without Men" was the
orchard in the city of Tehran.

00:27:42.310 --> 00:27:44.050
I think that's
the only way I can

00:27:44.050 --> 00:27:48.410
think in general about the
good and evil and all of that.

00:27:48.410 --> 00:27:51.470
And so I never see
anything in one way.

00:27:51.470 --> 00:27:53.740
